ber\/a-tribute-to-cozy-beyond-furnace-tune-ups\/\">A Tribute to Cozy: Beyond Furnace Tune-Ups<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Heating Maintenance in Carrollton, TX Schedule a Routine Heater Tune-Up with Our Team Today! The very best way to ensure optimal heating system performance and maximum energy efficiency is to schedule routine heating maintenance. An annual tune-up can significantly improve your system\u2019s ability to effectively heat your home, not to mention lower your energy bills [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":true},"service_category":[9],"class_list":["post-62","services","type-services","status-publish","hentry","service_category-heating"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v26.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Heating Maintenance - Medley<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"From AC repair to water heater installs, Medley delivers dependable heating, cooling, and plumbing services in Carrollton, TX. Your comfort is our priority.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/callmedley.com\/services\/heating-maintenance\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Heating Maintenance - Medley\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"From AC repair to water heater installs, Medley delivers dependable heating, cooling, and plumbing services in Carrollton, TX. Your comfort is our priority.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/callmedley.com\/services\/heating-maintenance\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Medley\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2025-07-28T00:08:20+00:00\" \/>\n<m